图片来源：Kyotonews“ 韩国新天地受害者团体宣布将以违反《传染病预防法》和《特定经济犯罪加重处罚法》对新天地总会长李万熙提起指控。
Source: Kyotonews.com "Korea's Xintiandi Victim Group has announced that it will sue Lee Wanxi, president of Xintiandi, for violating the Communicable Disease Prevention Act and the Act on Aggravating Punishment for Certain Economic Crimes.
”韩国中央防疫对策本部2月29日通报称，截至当天下午4时，韩国较当天上午9时新增219例新型冠状病毒确诊病例，累计确诊增至3150例。
The number of confirmed cases of coronavirus has risen to 3,150, with 219 new cases of coronavirus diagnosed since 9: 00 pm on the same day, the central government said on Tuesday.
中央灾难安全对策本部第一总括协调官金刚立29日在记者会上表示，新天地大邱教会信徒确诊感染新冠病毒的比例极高，预计大邱地区确诊病例今后几日内将持续增加。
The number of confirmed cases in Taegu Church in Xintiandi is very high, and the number of confirmed cases in Taegu district is expected to continue to increase in the coming days, Kim Gang-li, the First Omnibus Coordinator of the Central Committee for Disaster Security Response, told a news conference.
截至目前，拥有250万人口的韩国第四大城市大邱共确诊超2000例，占韩国全部病例的70%。
So far, Taegu, South Korea's fourth-largest city with a population of 2.5 million, has diagnosed more than 2,000 cases, accounting for 70% of all cases in the country.
金刚立还表示，前往筛查诊所接受检测的大邱市民被确诊的比例远远低于新天地信徒。
Mr Kim also said the proportion of Taegu residents diagnosed at screening clinics was far lower than that of Xintiandi.
据大邱市政府和医务人员透露，确诊病例中，80%以上病情较轻无需医学治疗，20%有呼吸道疾病症状而需要医学治疗，其中5%因基础疾病需要特别观察。
According to the municipality of Daegu and medical personnel, more than 80 per cent of the confirmed cases require no medical treatment, 20 per cent have symptoms of respiratory diseases and require medical treatment, 5 per cent of which require special observation because of basic diseases.
大邱市医师协会从昨日起根据患者病情的轻重程度，优先对重症患者进行住院治疗。
From yesterday, Daegu City Physicians' Association, according to the severity of the patient's illness, priority for severe hospital treatment.
金刚立表示，本周末将是疫情是否会进一步升级的关键时刻，呼吁民众尽量避免外出，暂停参与宗教活动和集会等聚集性活动。
Kim said the weekend would be a critical time for the epidemic to escalate further, calling on people to avoid going out and suspending participation in gatherings such as religious events and gatherings.
此外，韩国新天地受害者团体宣布将以违反《传染病预防法》和《特定经济犯罪加重处罚法》对新天地总会长李万熙提起指控。
In addition, the Korea Xintiandi Victim Group announced that charges would be brought against Lee Wanxi, the president of Xintiandi, for violating the Communicable Disease Prevention Act and the Act on Aggravating Punishment for Certain Economic Crimes.
水原检察厅已将此案分配至刑事六部展开调查。
The Suwon Prosecutor's Office has assigned the case to six criminal divisions for investigation.
受害者团体表示，新天地一直在欺瞒疾病管理本部。
Victim groups say Xintiandi has been deceiving the Department of Disease Control.
到目前为止，韩国已有17例患者病亡。
So far, 17 patients have died in South Korea.
29日新增一名死者为77岁韩国男性，患有糖尿病等基础疾病。
29, the death of a 77-year-old Korean male, diabetes and other basic diseases.
29日当天，韩国宣布首例出院后病毒检测又变成阳性的患者。
On the 29th, South Korea announced the first post-discharge virus detection has become positive patients.
这名73岁女性本月早些时候确诊，后于2月22日康复出院。
The 73-year-old woman was diagnosed earlier this month and recovered from hospital on February 22.
然而她在27日再次出现症状，28日再被发现感染。
However, she again on the 27th symptoms, 28 was found to be infected.
这名患者的儿子和儿媳近期曾到访中国广东省，两人都已确诊。
The patient's son and daughter-in-law recently visited Guangdong Province, China, and both have been confirmed.
而复阳患者表示在康复出院后她一直呆在室内。
The Fuyang patient said she stayed indoors after recovering and leaving the hospital.
与此同时，韩国庆尚北道金泉市监狱一名囚犯确诊感染新冠肺炎，这是韩国首次有监狱犯人感染。
Meanwhile, a South Korean inmate at Jinquan City Prison in Gyeongshan North Province has been diagnosed with pneumonia, the first time a prison inmate has been infected.
该名囚犯为60岁男性，出现呼吸道症状后被确诊。
The prisoner, a 60-year-old male, was diagnosed with respiratory symptoms.
该监狱已有31人被隔离。
Thirty-one people have been isolated from the prison.
据韩国《中央日报》消息，随着新型冠状病毒疫情扩散，韩国政府建议各种培训机构暂时停止营业，但目前首尔只有三分之一的培训班接受了政府建议。
As the new coronavirus has spread, the South Korean government has advised various training institutions to suspend operations, but only one-third of the courses in Seoul have accepted the government's offer, the China Daily reported.
首尔市教育厅的数据显示，在首尔市内2.5万家培训班和课外教学机构中，目前只有8670家停止营业。
Only 8,670 of the 25,000 training classes and extracurricular institutions in Seoul are now closed, according to Seoul's Education Department.
首尔市教育厅于2月24日向各类培训机构发出了暂时停业的建议。
On 24 February, the Seoul Metropolitan Department of Education issued recommendations to various training institutions to suspend operations.
根据现行法律，政府只能建议各类学校停课关闭，但不能采取强制措施。
Under the current law, the Government can only recommend that all types of schools be closed, but not by coercive measures.
